headline: Jabil, IBD Stock Of The Day, Plots 50% Surge In Data Center Business As AI Booms
summary: Jabil has left little doubt that data centers are its most important market, and it plans to take full advantage.  The electronics manufacturing company is the IBD Stock Of The Day.  Operating in 30 countries, Jabil is also an expert on supply chains.
